title: "Google to pay $700 mln to US consumers
source_name: "Alphabet's Google has agreed to pay $700 million and to allow for greater competition in its Play app store
date: according to the terms of an antitrust settlement with U.S. states and consumers disclosed on Monday in a San Francisco federal court."
